Plot.
The twins of Paul "Muad'dib" Atreides become embroiled in the political 
landscape of Arrakis ("Dune") and the rest of the universe. Focusing on 
the second and third novel. In this mini-series, a young man, Paul 
Atreides, moves with his family to a new planet known as Arrakis. Paul, 
his family and a number of political entities become embroiled in a 
confrontation that will change the course of humanity.
